snippet.title: 99 Cent Store Christmas Shopping Spree!
snippet.description:
MERRY CHRISTMAS AND HAPPY SHOPPING SPREE! lol

HI ANGELS - today I am taking you to the bargain hunter's dream, the 99 cent only store! Everything is a dollar and everyone is very rich in there, it's the shopping fantasy. So from home decor to outfits and everything you ever needed for the holidays, here is me losing my mind on a very extra shopping spree. 

I love you! Merry Christmas to all, and to all a good haul. 

3,447,000 kisses!
Xx
Amber :)
